{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a very, very heavy dress that I was perspiring day and night, you know, with that black dress.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I hate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The second time, you know, after, like, a few weeks, they take you to the showers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To the showers-- they give you a small bar of soap when you enter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you go to the showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the-- in the-- in the ceiling, you know, there were-- you know, sometimes it was water coming through.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sometimes, it was gas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So now, we went-- enter in this knowing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because sometimes we will die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometime, we will come back alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And before entering, no-- no-- no towels or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They will give you a bar of soap.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In this bar of soap, there were three initials-- in Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That, I forgot-- how to pronounce in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it means pure Jewish fat-- into the soap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was-- it meant that they were making the soap out of the corpse of the living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They make those soaps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were making out of the-- of the corpse of the living, many things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They will make, you know, that parchment, to make that-- to-- to-- to the lampshades.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They will make, you know, purses for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "For the skin of the dead people, they will make you beautiful skins, you know, like purses for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They will make anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The-- and then, the-- the-- the flesh, you know, they were-- sometimes, you know, when they burn-- if they were not burned, they will use it for-- to make sausages, and to make, you know, bologna-- that they were giving us at night to eat.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was you know, like you say me-- at the beginning we were very kosher.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
